  "clause": "Section 4.2 – Gifts and Hospitality: Employees may accept gifts of nominal value not exceeding $50 from vendors, provided the gift is not intended to influence a business decision. Any gift exceeding $50 must be reported and declined.",
  "section_number": "4.2",
  "policy_id": "ANTI-BRIBERY-001"
}
